      public GenericSortWithHelper(String description, Comparator<X> comparator, int N, int nRuns, Config config)
      Constructs a GenericSortWithHelper instance using a description, comparator, size, number of runs, and configuration. Creates a Helper with the specified parameters and initializes the GenericSortWithHelper.
      Parameters:
      description - a description of the sort method, used for identification purposes
      comparator - the comparator to define the order of the elements being sorted
      N - the size of the dataset to be sorted
      nRuns - the number of times the sorting process will be executed
      config - the configuration object to set up the Helper and related behavior
